  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Young man stabbed in fuel scuffle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A man who was attacked with a sharp weapon during an argument between two groups at the IOC petrol station in Matugama this afternoon has been admitted to hospital, Matugama Police said.",
        "The victim is a resident of Iddagoda, Deniya, Matugama, police said.",
        "The victim had been waiting in line at a petrol station near the Matugama Public Stadium when he was stabbed at around 3.30 pm, police said.",
        "The injured have been admitted to the Matugama Government Hospital with stab wounds to the abdomen, head and arms, a hospital spokesman said."
      ],
